#~ "Choose the default text editing component that you wish to use in "
#~ "&kwrite;. You can choose <guilabel>System Default</guilabel>, "
#~ "<guilabel>Embedded Advanced Text Editor</guilabel> or <guilabel>&Qt; "
#~ "Designer Based Text Editor</guilabel> (note that the &Qt; Designer Based "
#~ "Text Editor is only available if you have KDevelop installed on your "
